SupremacyNotes: Incite Fervour - all regiments lose Broken status and gain Devout for the turn except for Prioriy Commanders and their warbands.  Regiments cannot be broken that turn.

Restricted: Brute Drones|Vanguard Clone Infiltrators|Desolation Drones|Marksman Clones|Pteraphon
SupremacyNotes: Coordinated Assault - the top three cards get resolved consecutively
Living Metal - heal all regiments for four wounds
Enduring Mountain - regiments ignore 1 point of Cleave or 1 point of Armor Piercing from attacks this turn
Call the Hunt - regiments in warband gain flank
All enemy stands count clear shots as obstructed until end of the turn
